cast.overview: Amid a future war between the human race and the forces of artificial intelligence, a hardened ex-special forces agent grieving the disappearance of his wife, is recruited to hunt down and kill the Creator, the elusive architect of advanced AI who has developed a mysterious weapon with the power to end the war—and mankind itself.
cast.title: The Creator

cast.overview: A shaman's family learn that their goddess is supposedly controlling one of them. However, their lives take a frightening turn when they realise the goddess has nothing to do with the possession.
cast.title: The Medium

also_known_as: เอี้ยง สวนีย์ อุทุมมา
details.biography:
Iang Sawanee Utoomma is a performer, theatre director and playwright.

Sawanee became particularly well-known for her role in the award-winning 2021 Thai-Korean horror film 'The Medium' for which she won Best Supporting Actress at the 30th Suphannahong National Film Awards.
details.name: Sawanee Utoomma
